source:
TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_SEQ_00 Quest Sync
The hasty hunter remembers how helpful you can be.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_SEQ_00 Quest Sync
The hasty hunter remembers how helpful you can be.

source: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_TODO_00<tab>Slay a cracked Ronkan doll for its core.
target: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_TODO_00<tab>Slay a cracked Ronkan doll for its core.

source: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the core to the hasty hunter.
target: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the core to the hasty hunter.

source: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_FANOWHUNTER03477_000_000<tab>A welcome sight in my hour of need.
target: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_FANOWHUNTER03477_000_000<tab>A welcome sight in my hour of need.

source: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_FANOWHUNTER03477_000_001<tab>As you know, a number of our stone sentinels have turned against us. But if they can be slain, they may yet serve to protect these ruins.
target: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_FANOWHUNTER03477_000_001<tab>As you know, a number of our stone sentinels have turned against us. But if they can be slain, they may yet serve to protect these ruins.

source: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_FANOWHUNTER03477_000_002<tab>We lack the knowledge to build more, but it is possible to use their parts to repair those that yet remain.
target: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_FANOWHUNTER03477_000_002<tab>We lack the knowledge to build more, but it is possible to use their parts to repair those that yet remain.

source: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_FANOWHUNTER03477_000_003<tab>If you could slay even a single sentinel and bring me its core, that is all I require to begin my work.
target: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_FANOWHUNTER03477_000_003<tab>If you could slay even a single sentinel and bring me its core, that is all I require to begin my work.

source: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_FANOWHUNTER03477_000_004<tab>I only require a single core to begin my work.
target: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_FANOWHUNTER03477_000_004<tab>I only require a single core to begin my work.

source: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_FANOWHUNTER03477_000_012<tab>As I said before, we lack the knowledge to build the sentinels. And this is perhaps the most difficult piece to replicate.
target: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_FANOWHUNTER03477_000_012<tab>As I said before, we lack the knowledge to build the sentinels. And this is perhaps the most difficult piece to replicate.

source: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_FANOWHUNTER03477_000_013<tab>So long as their cores can be retrieved, we can prolong the life of those we yet have.
target: TEXT_LUCKZF018_03477_FANOWHUNTER03477_000_013<tab>So long as their cores can be retrieved, we can prolong the life of those we yet have.
